---

<section class="scroll-reveal w-full flex justify-center" aria-label="Open source projects">
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1020px] mt-section mb-section px-5 max-sm:px-0">
    <p class="m-0 text-xl leading-[2] text-black">
      As developers, we&#x27;re commit to make the world a better place by opensourcing as much as we can.
      We have sponsored numerous community event including{' '}
      <a href="https://hkoscon.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Hong Kong Open Source Conference</a>,{' '}
      <a href="https://tw.pycon.org/2015apac/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">PyCon APAC 2015</a>,{' '}
      <a href="http://sitcon.org/2016/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">SITCON 2016</a> etc.
      <br /><br />
      Beside contribute to other open-source project regularly, here are some small open source project our team
      release over the year. If you&#x27;re interested, check out our{' '}
      <a href="https://code.oursky.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Code Blog</a> too.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-section mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-black">Kubernetes / CI</h2>
    <p class="m-0 text-xl leading-[2] text-black">
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/kubernetes-github-authn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">kubernetes-github-authn</a> — GitHub token authentication for Kubernetes<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/devsecops-ci" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">devsecops-ci</a> — DevSecOps implementation at Oursky, provide a easy to invoke checker toolset to enhance security quality automatically<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/flutter-docker" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">flutter-docker</a> — Dockerfile for building docker image in CI use.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/devsecops-secret" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">devsecops-secret</a> — secret generators for CI and dev env.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/devsecops-ignore" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">DevSecOps-ignore</a> — scan all repository within organization, that for each repository if there is ignore files, that file should contains basic ignore entries.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/travis-ios-script" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">travis-ios-script</a> — Reusable iOS Script for Travis CI integration with Testflight, Crittercism and HockeyApp support.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/gogocyclo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">gogocyclo</a> — Tool intended to be used in CI to ignore certain results from gocyclo.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/slack-dsym-bot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">slack-dsym-bot</a> — Slackbot for iOS crash report via Sentry.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-section mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-black">Web / Mobile</h2>
    <p class="m-0 text-xl leading-[2] text-black">
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/react-native-oursky" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">react-native-oursky</a> — React Native Scaffolding commonly used by Ourskyers.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/react-messageformat" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">react-messageformat</a> — Provide better React apps internationalization.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/Redux" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Redux</a> — Swift implementation of redux
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-section mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-black">Other Tools</h2>
    <p class="m-0 text-xl leading-[2] text-black">
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/gh-html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">gh-html</a> — Github Pages alike for private repository.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/aws-site-manager" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">aws-site-manager</a> — Very simple CLI to create S3/Cloudfront Static Website.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/dotfiles" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">dotfiles</a> — Various dotfiles suggest to use company-wide.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/parse-server-sendgrid-adapter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">parse-server-sendgrid-adapter</a> — Simple sendgrid adapter for parse server.<br />
      <a href="https://github.com/oursky/norecaptcha" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">norecaptcha</a> — Python client for the google new No CAPTCHA reCAPTCHA services.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
